content: Should CatalogEntry be listed twice on build.fhir.org/resourcelist.html ?

I assume you mean on the Categorized view? The question is whether it should show up under Documents. It's used as a part of a catalog (obviously), which is a document. But I don't know if that means it makes sense to list it there. I think where it is under Specialized is probably sufficient, so it could probably be removed from Documents. I was on the call today, but of course we didn't discuss that in particular.
yes there. I do not think it's a definitional artefact
Well, actually I agree with that. But it's also not a document.
Or maybe just leave it in Documents, since it has some relation there.
